  "title": "Project Engineer (Building Construction/Industrial Warehouse Building/A1 Main Con)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Review specifications, clarifications, and drawings.</li>\n  <li>Schedule works, requisition materials, control costs, and supervise projects.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with Structural, Architectural, and M&amp;E teams to resolve issues.</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely progress and compliance with safety and regulations.</li>\n  <li>Conduct QA/QC and enforce safety on-site.</li>\n  <li>Prepare progress and handover reports.</li>\n  <li>Handle additional assigned tasks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Civil Engineering with PEB recognition.</li>\n  <li>Working experience in A1/A2 building companies is preferred. </li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>_______________________________________________________</strong></p>\n<p><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on “Quick Apply” or contact win@hkmsvs.com for more details.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</strong></p>\n<p><strong>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</strong></p>\n<p><strong>3) Expected salary</strong></p>\n<p><strong>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</strong></p>\n<p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Wee Wai Dan</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA License No : 03C5391</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA Reg No : R22109628</strong></p>",
